Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who'll be\NKing of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm is coming.\NAn unimaginably big storm is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:02:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all coincidences?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if heaven is trying\Nto let that man live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry\Nor we'll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna make it to\Nthe Grand Line like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Legend Has Started!\NHead For The Grand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate, huh? Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this storm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't leave soon,\Nwe'll be stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san was right when she said\Nwe should hurry back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Move:\NMy Carnival of Colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking me is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a man alive\Nwho can touch my smooth skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a second there,\NI saw a field filled with flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, Captain Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy, this isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're marines from headquarters.\NThere'll be no end to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. I could care less if the\Nmarines want to stick their nose into...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose nose did you say is sticking out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum! Go after Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji and Richie should have\Nburned down his ship by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't get off of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll kick his ass and\Nleave this island, guys!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Buggy! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igniting the bomb engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Big Sis Alvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No friction...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:05:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth-Smooth Tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the pirates get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What's this smoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for you, small fries!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the power\Nof Plume-Plume Fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took down Buggy's\Ngang in a split second...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! He caught\Nus all in one fell swoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this annoying steel net?!\NFiring a weird pistol like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a "Cage Shot" developed by\Nthe Navy to deal with Devil Fruit powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring my Billower Bike here!\NWe'll go after Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy might be\Nalready heading toward it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get out as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Nami!\NCan't I just ditch this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't! Run faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What's with\Nthis sudden downpour,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we have to burn down this ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This is bad, Richie!\NWe can't get a fire going like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient, Richie! I'll feed you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, sneak thief woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:07:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Fresh Egg Star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! The rain made my hand slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!! You're such a...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Let's get on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! You have to get past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mohji, Vice-Captain of\Nthe Buggy the Clown Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you take\None step on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the cannon unit!\NWe'll capture the pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--N-N-N-Nami!!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction is the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell where we're going\Nbecause of this heavy rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What persistent bastards!\NShould we stop and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize you're Roronoa Zoro,\Nand a pirate to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna take this sword, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What'd you do to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't ask my name. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rogue like you can't be\Nallowed to own a renowned sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll collect your sword,\Nthe legendary Wado Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! How dare you attack a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please don't interfere!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fight between Roronoa\Nand me! There's no need to step in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her. Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! If you hurt the\Nlady, I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you have this\Nsword no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major Tashigi lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Sergeant Major Tashigi lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... I'm in a hurry, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you finishing me off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Zoro. You're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's humiliating that\Nyou won't fight seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a game played in earnest just because\Nmen're physically stronger than women!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you don't understand the\Nfeeling that I wish I was born a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't carry a sword for pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like your very being!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Your face! It looks exactly like\Nmy close friend's who died long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, you started saying\Nthe same thing she used to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't imitate, you copycat woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Stop talking\Nlike a child! You're rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live the way I am! I don't\Nknow what your friend was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm the one who feels upset!\NIsn't she the copycat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the exit! The harbor is up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:12:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that you can't enter\Nthe Grand Line unless you beat me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an airhead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, go on ahead. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know about that.\NThis is the end for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:13:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here any longer,\Nthe Going Merry will be sunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you going to set sail?\NLuffy and the others aren't here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any other choice!\NIt's better than getting sunk here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right rudder full!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what're we going to do\Nabout Luffy and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pick them up somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away! Follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're Luffy and Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we collect those damn idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:14:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This is endless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover his back! Get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We can't head back to land\Nbecause of the strong current.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Usopp!\N--Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you and\Nenter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who'll be\NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your idle talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the Plume Plume Fruit.\NSo my body becomes smoke at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Finished already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ahh, that's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get it? You can't\Neven enter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted for a 30 million Berry bounty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're running out of your devil's luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? Who's that? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government wants your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is waiting for our answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry up or the\Nship will be swept away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wha?!\N--W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man...\NWhat was that sudden gust?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He appeared and disappeared\Nlike lighting on the same day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Gold Roger was executed\N22 years ago. What on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who'll be\NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's your decision, then go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did you\Nhelp that man... Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What reason would there be to\Ninterfere with a man's departure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail! We'll go after Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll enter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, Captain! This island\Nis in your jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what\Nthe higher-ups would say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them I said,\N"Don't give me orders."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive Roronoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll capture him without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, that flashy gust was lucky for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to escape like\Nthis because I always behave well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're we going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Grand Line.\N--The Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is a good opportunity. I have\Nto settle with that damn rubber man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head straight into\Nthe nostalgic Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! It's almost like\Nthe ship's gonna tip over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a lighthouse of the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a "guiding light." The entrance to\Nthe Grand Line lies ahead of that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Line is ahead of that light...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But there's no reason to\Nenter during a storm like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we hold a launching ceremony\Nfor setting sail on the great ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to find the All Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become\Na master swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to draw a world map!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:22:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In order... to become\Na brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going... to the Grand Line!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's going on over there?\NA flock of birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.98,0:24:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be fish under that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.65,0:24:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch some, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? It's not fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.32,0:24:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble! I see a Navy fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did they come to capture me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.32,0:24:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! They're firing at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.32,0:24:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.66,0:24:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Precursor to a New Adventure!\NApis, a Mysterious Girl"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
